Attribution
-----------
The lexicon is derived from the Korean Sentiment Analysis Corpus (KOSAC),
developed at Seoul National University. The morpheme N-gram lexicon was
constructed and released by Sumin Park (2016).

When you redistribute or build upon this data you must:
  - give appropriate credit to KOSAC and to the lexicon author, and
  - distribute your contributions under the same CC BY-SA 4.0 license.
